{
  "texts": [
    "The fine-tuning datasets for each variable were divided into a 70% training set and a 30% validation set.",
    "Hyperparameters were tuned using 10fold cross-validation on 70% of the training data to maximize the area under the receiver operating curve (AUC).",
    "We selected a range of variables for each hyperparameter and performed a grid search to find the best hyperparameter configurations.",
    "Our grid search included learning rate (5e-5, 3e-5, 2e-5), batch size (8, 16, 32), number of training epochs (4, 5, 10), and weight decay (0.01, 0.05, 0.1).",
    "The final models were fine-tuned on 100% of the fine-tuning dataset."
  ]
}